        "heading": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<strong>MacBook Air Repair — Expert Service in London<\/strong>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The MacBook Air is Apple's most popular laptop — and one of the most common repairs we carry out in London. From cracked Retina displays to swollen batteries, charging faults, and liquid damage, we handle every MacBook Air repair at component level. Same-day express repair is available for most common faults. All repairs come with a 2-year warranty.<\/p>"
